    <!-- Information We Collect -->
    <h4 id="information-we-collect">Information We Collect</h4>
    <p>We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, and any other details you provide when contacting us or using our services. We also collect information about your usage of our website through cookies and other tracking technologies.</p>

    <!-- How We Use Your Information -->
    <h4 id="how-we-use-your-information">How We Use Your Information</h4>
    <p>We use the information collected to provide you with our services, respond to your inquiries, improve our website, and communicate important updates. We do not sell or share your information with third parties except as required by law.</p>

    <!-- Cookies -->
    <h4 id="cookies">Cookies</h4>
    <p>Our website uses cookies to improve your experience. Cookies are small files stored on your device that help us understand how you interact with our site, allowing us to provide better services and more personalized content. You can disable cookies through your browser settings, but some parts of the site may not function properly if you do so.</p>
    <p>If you wish to opt out of non-essential cookies, you may <a href="/cookie-settings">manage your cookie preferences here</a>.</p>

    <!-- Data Security -->
    <h4 id="data-security">Data Security</h4>
    <p>We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information. Access to personal data is restricted to authorized personnel only, and we use secure technology to safeguard the information we collect.</p>

    <!-- GDPR Compliance -->
    <h4 id="gdpr-compliance">Your Rights Under GDPR</h4>
    <p>If you are a resident of the European Economic Area (EEA), you have certain data protection rights under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). These include the right to access, correct, or delete personal information we hold about you. If you wish to exercise these rights, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>

    <!-- Your Consent -->
    <h4 id="your-consent">Your Consent</h4>
    <p>By using our website, you consent to our Privacy Policy. If we make any changes to our Privacy Policy, we will update the content on this page accordingly. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.</p>

    <!-- Contact Us -->
